Date: Wed, 8 Jul 2026 14:08:09 +0900
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] binder: test: add CPU topology-tiered latency tracking to
 schd-dbg

Introduce `CpuTopologyInfo` and `TieredStats` to classify and measure Binder
IPC latency based on CPU tiers (same_core, same_cluster, cross_cluster).  This
allows more granular scheduling behavior analysis in schd-dbg.

Change-Id: Ib0c7b737d49cdd0c41baca3052823b73eaf2f670
Signed-off-by: trieu2.huynh <trieu2.huynh@lge.corp-partner.google.com>
